name: PlexussCollegeAnswers
0:
”Alexa open plexuss”
”Alexa, ask plexuss to how many people apply to john brown university?”
”Alexa, ask plexuss to where is ucla located”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: plexuss
Developer Terms of Use
des: Ask any questions regarding any university in the United States. You can ask about the history of a college, admission stats, cost, admission date, is the school private or public, for-profit or nonprofit, 2 year or 4-year school, is the college religiously affiliated, semester or quarter system, number of students, number of applicants, percentage of applicants accepted and enrolled, application fee, undergraduate versus graduate degrees, number of transfer students, number of full-time students, number of part-time students, percentage of Native Americans, % of Asian American Students, % of Black Students, Percentage of Hispanic Students, % of Native Hawaiian or Pacific Islander, % of white students, number of international students, University tuition, out of state tuition, cost of room and board, CLEP offering, First-year retention rate, Financial aid data, what SAT score is required, what ACT score is needed, university undergraduate ranking, university ranking by major, undergraduate ranking, graduate ranking, ranking nationally, ranking within a state, AP credit policy, college accommodation, ROTC program, Online degree offers, loan default rate, study abroad program, sports programs, football team, basketball team, baseball team, cross country teams, college veteran benefits, books and supplies and much more.
priv:
